cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.CY 

This paper is about generating natural language explanations for autonomous system behavior using neural machine translation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves natural language processing, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks for translation makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper also involves human-computer interaction, which suggests that it could belong to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper involves game playing, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
